# üíä DHL Pharmacy - POS & Management System

DHL Pharmacy is a full-featured **Pharmacy Point of Sale and Management System** built using the **MERN Stack (MongoDB, Express, React, Node.js)**.  
It helps pharmacies manage daily operations including products, stock batches, sales, employee payrolls, and expiration alerts ‚Äî all in one system.

---

## ‚≠ê Key Features

| Area | Features |
|------|----------|
| **Authentication & Roles** | Secure login with Admin, Cashier, and Finance roles |
| **Product Management** | Add, edit, delete products and assign categories |
| **Batch & Inventory Control** | Track quantities, expiry dates, and auto-alerts |
| **POS System** | Smooth transaction process for cashiers with invoice generation |
| **Alerts Dashboard** | Alerts for **low stock**, **expired**, and **soon-to-expire** meds |
| **Payroll System** | Manage employee salaries, deductions, and payments |
| **Reports & Insights** | View daily sales and business summaries |

---

## üõ†Ô∏è Tech Stack

### Frontend
- React.js
- React Router
- Axios
- **Bootstrap** + Custom CSS

### Backend
- Node.js
- Express.js
- MongoDB & Mongoose
- JSON Web Token (JWT) Authentication
- bcrypt (secure password hashing)

